<emphasis bold="true" box="[1155,1211,1340,1365]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Legs</emphasis>
: Similar to female. Tibia and posterior basitarsus 4.5 times longer than wide. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[805,929,1375,1400]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Metasoma</emphasis>
