<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="417" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,151,1869]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1663,1688]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species, one of the most elegant Mesoamerican 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[973,1065,1664,1688]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="417" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[973,1065,1664,1688]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Colletes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, is dedicated to Isabel Aguilar, mother of the first author.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="417" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,151,1869]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1735,1760]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Distribution.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Ayala, 2017" authorityName="Ayala" authorityYear="2017" box="[359,551,1736,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="417" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="isabelae" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[359,551,1736,1760]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">Colletes isabelae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[557,621,1735,1760]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[557,621,1735,1760]" pageId="16" pageNumber="417">sp. n.</emphasis>
